::Dark One/Nemesis Enforcer::

Dark One growls as he hears Tavatron's words. He walks over to the femm, 
bending down to look her in the eyes, his eyes full of evil.

"Pathetic, eh?" he asks, laughing, "I'm not the one strapped to that table."

"Would you rather be?" Nemesis says, smiling.

Dark One turns around, taking out a pistol and aiming it at Nemesis, "Do you 
want to repeat that?"

"Don't do anything stupid," Nemesis' smile disapears, "I am second in 
command. With one word, you'll have autoguns slaggin' you in no time."

Dark One growls. "Allright," he says, lowering the gun, "Consider yourself 
lucky."
